{"tid":1009340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★派4000蚊首5日收近20萬申請　新增3地點領現金支票","createTime":"2019-02-05T06:06:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T06:25:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"677dc6451914d27d6edd89bde041d9b622625bfc","tid":1009340,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T06:06:02.000Z","msg":"政府派4000港元關愛共享計劃由2月1日起至4月30日接受合資格市民申請。政務司司長張建宗今早(5日)出席林村許節活動時表示，政府現時已收到10萬至20萬份申請表。針對沒銀行戶口申請者領取現金支票安排，張指現時除了觀塘「職津處」辦事處可以領取外，其餘3個地區分區辦事處亦可領取，地點分別位於長沙灣、旺角及啟德，同時政府增加查詢熱線至60條線，有需要時致電政府熱線1823亦會支援市民查詢計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190205/bkn-20190205115046919-0205_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190205%2Fbkn-20190205115046919-0205_00822_001.html&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=ef2c2ccb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190205/bkn-20190205115046919-0205_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9be85120c36b114750314ade677fb4a7f773d052","tid":1009340,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T06:06:09.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"1c7a07ab8ca088aaa63ddb7c3f86f26b013ae095","tid":1009340,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T06:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0ee9c4f3b4c1572421f9d92fa2c6aa9a2de3fb","tid":1009340,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T06:19:13.000Z","msg":"唔係3月尾截止？"},{"pid":"c4c4558c723d662ec704ee0acbe82d70e50b96fd","tid":1009340,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac0ee9c4f3b4c1572421f9d92fa2c6aa9a2de3fb","tid":1009340,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T06:19:13.000Z","msg":"唔係3月尾截止？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T06:22:41.000Z","msg":"4月30"},{"pid":"3b5c0c33366353e5892dba6d3ed4d6a88763a